  "short_description": "MikroTik wAP ac LTE kit (2024) - weatherproof outdoor wireless access point with built-in LTE modem, dual-band 2.4/5 GHz Wi-Fi (WiFi 5), 2x 1 Gbps RJ45 ports, miniPCI-e slot",
  "description": "Expand your wireless network outdoors and enjoy seamless internet connectivity with the new MikroTik wAP ac LTE kit (2024). This versatile device combines a high-performance outdoor wireless access point with a built-in LTE modem, offering a reliable solution for homes, offices, and even remote locations. Enjoy seamless wireless connectivity indoors and outdoors. The wAP ac supports both 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz bands, offering wider coverage and reduced interference for your devices. The built-in LTE connectivity provides a reliable internet backup option or primary internet access in areas with limited wired internet availability.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Outdoor Wireless & Cellular Connectivity",
      "text": "Expand your wireless network outdoors and enjoy seamless internet connectivity with the new MikroTik wAP ac LTE kit (2024). This versatile device combines a high-performance outdoor wireless access point with a built-in LTE modem, offering a reliable solution for homes, offices, and even remote locations. Enjoy seamless wireless connectivity indoors and outdoors. The wAP ac supports both 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz bands, offering wider coverage and reduced interference for your devices. The built-in LTE connectivity provides a reliable internet backup option or primary internet access in areas with limited wired internet availability."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Power and Performance",
      "text": "The wAP ac LTE kit (2024) is equipped with a powerful quad-core CPU (IPQ-4018) that delivers smooth performance for handling demanding wireless applications. Two Gigabit Ethernet ports enable wired connections to your network devices, offering maximum speed and performance. MikroTik's RouterOS operating system offers a wide range of features and functionalities for advanced network configuration, security, and management. Upgrade your outdoor connectivity with the MikroTik wAP ac LTE kit (2024) and experience the power of combined Wi-Fi and cellular technology."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Reliable connectivity in any conditions",
      "text": "The wAP ac LTE kit (2024) boasts a robust, weatherproof design that can withstand extreme temperatures ranging from -30°C to +60°C. This makes it perfect for outdoor deployments, whether you need internet access on your patio, connectivity in a remote cabin, or reliable Wi-Fi for your garden office. Mount the wAP ac LTE kit (2024) virtually anywhere with its versatile mounting design. Attach it to a wall, ceiling, pole, or mast for optimal signal distribution in your desired location. The MikroTik wAP ac LTE kit (2024) is the perfect solution for extending Wi-Fi coverage to outdoor areas and providing internet access in remote locations."
    }
  ],
